Procedure:
1.	Create a lex specification file to recognize tokens in the grammar
2.	Create a Yacc specification file to parse the tokens in the grammar
3.	Compile lex and yacc files to generate C files
4.	Now compile both the c files using C compiler to get executable file
5.	Run the executable file to get the desired output by providing necessary input

